"title": "5134: blindness, natural",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5134: blindness, natural",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The inability to see properly. The healing of such physical blindness was one of the many miracles performed by Jesus Christ, who restored sight to the blind at several points during his ministry. Scripture often treats blindness as a symbol of the human inability or refusal to realise the importance of God and the gospel. The restoration of sight can thus be treated as a symbol of coming to faith.</p>\n<h2>The causes of blindness</h2>\n<h3>A natural affliction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:11\">EXO 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:1\">GEN 27:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:17\">GEN 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:2\">1SA 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:15\">1SA 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1-John9:3\">JHN 9:1–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:11\">ACT 22:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:15\">GAL 4:15</a></p>\n<h3>A consequence of sin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:11\">GEN 19:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:28-Deut28:29\">DEU 28:28–28:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:18\">2KI 6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:23\">PSA 69:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:9-Acts13:11\">ACT 13:9–13:11</a></p>\n<h3>A result of human cruelty</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:14\">NUM 16:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:7\">2KI 25:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:7\">JER 39:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:11\">JER 52:11</a></p>\n<h2>Directions to care for the blind</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:14\">LEV 19:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:18\">DEU 27:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:15\">JOB 29:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:8\">JER 31:8</a></p>\n<h2>The healing of blindness</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:13\">LUK 14:13</a></p>\n<h3>The LORD makes blind eyes see</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:20\">2KI 6:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:8\">PSA 146:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:5\">ISA 35:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a></p>\n<h3>The healing of the blind by Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:30\">MAT 9:27–9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:5\">MAT 11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:21-Luke7:22\">LUK 7:21–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:30-Matt15:31\">MAT 15:30–15:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:29-Matt20:34\">MAT 20:29–20:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:46-Mark10:52\">MRK 10:46–10:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:35-Luke18:43\">LUK 18:35–18:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:22-Mark8:25\">MRK 8:22–8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:6-John9:7\">JHN 9:6–9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17-Acts9:18\">ACT 9:17–9:18</a> <em>through Ananias</em></p>\n<h2>Blindness as a symbol</h2>\n<h3>Of moral defect</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:4\">LEV 20:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:19\">DEU 16:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:3\">1SA 12:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">PRO 28:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29\">MAT 5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:23\">MAT 6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:9\">MAT 18:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:39\">LUK 6:39</a></p>\n<h3>Of grief</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:19\">GEN 21:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:33\">1SA 2:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:7\">JOB 17:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:7\">PSA 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9\">PSA 31:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:10\">PSA 38:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:9\">PSA 88:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:14\">ISA 38:14</a></p>\n<h3>Of the powerlessness of idols</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:5\">PSA 115:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:16\">PSA 135:16</a></p>",
